confirmDelivery(uint256).details: 이 함수가 호출되면, 판매자는 분쟁 제기 기간을 기다릴 필요 없이 즉시 자금을 인출할 수 있습니다.

params._coordinator: The address of the Orakl Coordinator contract.
params._initialOwner: The initial owner of the contract.
params._stableKRWAddress: The address of the StableKRW (ERC20) token contract.
params._trackingApiKey: The api key for tracking delivery.

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby disabling any functionality that is only available to the owner.

params._refundToBuyer: True to refund the buyer, false to pay the seller.
params._tradeId: The ID of the trade in dispute.

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

withdraw(uint256).details: 아래 두 가지 조건 중 하나를 만족하면 인출이 가능합니다: 1. 구매자가 수령 확인을 하여 거래 상태가 'Completed'가 된 경우 (즉시 인출 가능) 2. 거래 상태가 'Delivered'이고, 분쟁 제기 기간이 만료된 경우 (구매자 무응답 시)

confirmDelivery(uint256).notice: 구매자가 상품을 정상적으로 수령했음을 확인하는 함수입니다.

resolveDispute(uint256,bool).notice: Resolves a dispute. Can only be called by the owner.
